          <p class='first-para'>
            Order. I express the hope to the hon. Gentleman that he will refer, if only briefly, to the ombudsman.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0351P0-04435'>
        <a name='S6CV0351P0_20000607_WH_76'>  </a>
